1) Securities Regulation [LL4055/LL5055/LL6055]; 
(2) Corporate Law & Finance [LL4188/LL5188/LLD5188/LL6188];  
(3) Corporate Finance Law & Practice in Singapore [LL4182/LL5182/LLD5182/LL6182];  
(4) International Corporate Finance [LL4409/LL5409/LL6409]
